{
  "id": "adv_main_04_03_03",
  "title": "星空編1章13話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_garden-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_garden-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ……？\nこんな時間に私達を呼び出すなんて、どうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire…?\nWhat's the reason for calling us‚ at this hour?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "急にごめんね\nどうしても、二人とちゃんと話したかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for the sudden call\nSomehow‚ I wanted to talk to you two properly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "気にせんでええよ\nうちも会って話したいと思ってたところやから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry about it\nI've been wanting to meet and talk with you too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あのね、話って言うのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ what I want to talk about is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9573696296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "待って\n話を始める前に、私から言っておきたいことがあるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait\nBefore we start talking‚ there's something I want to say",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 29.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "昨日のライブバトル……負けたのは私のせいよ\n私が二人を引っ張っていかなきゃいけなかったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yesterday's live battle… it was my fault that we lost\nI had to lead you two…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "センターの私が不甲斐ないせいで\n悔しい思いをさせてしまって、本当にごめんなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so sorry that I made you feel so frustrated\nbecause of my pathetic leadership as the center",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "何言うてるん\n瑠依ちゃんは悪いことあらへん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about?\nRui-chan did nothing wrong…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんは最高のセンターや。そんな瑠依ちゃんを\nうちは支えるどころか、守られるばかりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan is the best center. Rather than supporting Rui-chan‚\nI was only protected by you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "誰かのせいで負けたとしたら\nそれはろくに支えられんかったうちのせいや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we lost because of someone else‚\nit's my fault for not supporting you properly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんは役立たずなんかじゃないよ！\nいつも私達のことをよく見て、気遣ってくれて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't Yu-chan's fault!\nYou always looking after us‚ caring for us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんが真っ先に気付いて、提案してくれるから\nトリエルのステージはどんどん良くなっていったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu-chan was the first to notice‚ made suggestions‚\nso TRINITYAiLE's stage got better and better",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0000020345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "もし誰かが悪いとしたら、それは私だよ\n一番足を引っ張っていたのは絶対私だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If anyone's to fault‚ it's me\nIt's definitely that I'm the one holding you back the most",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.2666656495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "すみれが悪い訳ないでしょ。すみれの明るさと優しさに\n私達がどれだけ救われていたか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not Sumire's fault. How much we have benefited\nfrom Sumire's brightness and kindness…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.1666656495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 92.6458497445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "悪いのは私よ\nセンターの私が力不足だったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's my fault\nI wasn't strong enough as the center…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.4999989828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃう、悪いのはうちや！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ it's me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.2227206469,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "悪いのは私だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was my fault!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1421744267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "いいえ、一番悪いのは私――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I'm the one who's most――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6205917119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "あーもう！　じゃあ、負けたのはみんなのせい！\n三人とも悪くない！　はい、この話はこれで終わり！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ohー come on! So‚ it's everyone's fault that we lost!\nNone of the three of us are at fault! Here‚ that's the end of this story!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.0333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_achieve-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 115.666670227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "……せやな\n一番悪いのは誰かなんて、考えても不毛なだけや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right\nIt's pointless to think about who's most at fault",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、負けた責任はリーダーの私に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ responsibility lies with me as the leader…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.0810923415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "リーダーもセンターも世間の目も関係あらへん\nトリエルは三人が並んで前に進むグループや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who is Leader‚ who is center‚ and public opinion are irrelevant\nTRINITYAiLE is a group of three moving forward together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7333368937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "勝っても負けても責任はうちら全員にある\nせやから、瑠依ちゃんが全部背負う必要はないんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Win or lose‚ we all share the responsibility\nRight‚ Rui-chan. You don't need to shoulder all the responsibility.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0000035603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ、瑠依ちゃん。一人で頑張らなくていいんだよ\n私達は三人でTRINITYAiLEなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right‚ Rui-chan. You don't have to do it alone\nWe are TRINITYAiLE‚ the three of us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.1000035603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "優……すみれ……\n……そうね、二人の言う通りだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu… Sumire…\n…That's right‚ you two are right",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.466670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "私、自分が思っていた以上に\nサニピに負けたのがショックだったのかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think‚ losing to Sunny Peace\nwas more of a shock to me than I thought",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5000035603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "負けたのは誰かのせいだなんて\nそんな風に考えてしまうくらい心が弱っていたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My mind becomes so weak that I think\nit's someone else's fault or something like that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.866670227,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "あんな負け方をしたんだから仕方ないよ\nでも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can't be helped‚ after how badly we lost\nBut…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.3333399454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tri-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 176.1000035603
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03/sud_vo_adv_main_04_03_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、ちゃんと負けを受け入れて前に進むわ\n……二人とも、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
